    <description>The `ViewEditMode` module controls the state of DetailView.ViewEditMode. Choose `Edit` mode to open a `DetailView` in edit mode. 

The module uses the next two strategies:
1. It monitors the `DetailView` creation and modifies its ViewEditMode property according to model configuration. However later ViewEditMode property modifications are allowed.
2. It monitors the `ViewEditMode` modifiation and cancels it if the `LockViewEditMode` attribute is used.</description>
